I have been having a very difficult time finding the words to express my feelings at this time in the midst of this sudden loss. I am deeply saddened to share the passing of Skyfall and Heartist Foundation co-founder, brother, co-writer, co-producer Craig Wilson. Craig was a champion for every artist he worked with and every person he knew. He lead with kindness in everything he did and was one of the hardest working people in this industry. His absence leaves a huge loss in all our hearts and in the music community. His music and vision will always live on.

Another official GRAMMY® nomination!

I am so honored and thankful to contribute to this record. When @curtis.stewart_violin brought me on to be a part of this amazing project—I flew to Hawaii and went into a deep creative space and would work on the album every morning at sunrise. I remember being deeply moved by the music and knew it would go on to do great things. Contributing to this record allowed me to integrate so many different aspects of what I do musically that I’ve cultivated throughout my life - see you at the GRAMMY Awards 2024!
Co created a special rendition of this classic Mariah Carey Christmas hit with @knowledjofficial who has toured with Mariah and the one and only @eliseharpermusic!
